To install docker ce in rhel first configure yum inside /etc/yum.repos.d

and then create a new file 


and then go to the rpm link for docker ce and copy it


then open the docker.repo file

[docker]
baseurl=https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/7/x86_64/stable/
gpgcheck=0


then execute the command

yum install docker-ce --nobest

Your docker will be installed in RHEL
